11212.content: You are bored one day and decide to go to your friend Ami's house. "Oh, hello Zip", she says as she opens the door. "What are you doing here?" "I got bored, so I wanted to hang out with you", you reply. You already know that Ami is Sailor Mercury, but the other Sailor Senshi don't know that you know. So you really weren't surprised to see Ami in her Sailor Senshi outfit. "I've got a 'little' surprise for you", Sailor Mercury tells you. "Close your eyes." You do as you are told. You start to feel a bit strange. When you open your eyes again, you are...
11212.title: Zip

112122.content:
"Ami! What the hell", you shout. Unfortunately, Sailor Mercury can't hear you at that size. "DON'T WORRY", she soothes. "I WON'T HURT YOU. I PROMISE." You know she won't hurt you, but you're still scared being that size. Sailor Mercury suddenly lowers her ear down to hear you. "Why'd you shrink me", you cry. "I JUST WANTED TO SEE IF MY SHRINK RAY WORKED", she responded. "UNFORTUNATELY, I DON'T KNOW HOW TO CHANGE YOU BACK AT THE MOMENT." As soon as you hear this, you start to sob. Sailor Mercury heard you crying and got up. She came back, holding a pair of tweezers. "GRAB ON", she tells you. She then carefully places you on a table. Then she leans forward to give you a kiss. You embrace her large lips as her warm breathe surrounds you. After that, she changes into her pajamas, places you on her nightstand, and goes to sleep.

In the middle of the night, you woke up and noticed that Ami was fast asleep. An idea popped into your head. You kinda liked Ami and wanted to get closer to her.
112122.title: ...almost the size of a speck.

1121222.content: You leap off of the nightstand and successfully land on Ami's bed. She was covered from her shoulders to her feet with a blanket, but you saw a small opening you could crawl under. Once under the blanket, you first decided to explore her...
1121222.title: Take a leap of faith

11212222.content: Is Ami sleeping on her back or her stomach?
11212222.title: ...panties.

You stop when you feel a large hole in front of you, and you realize you are near Ami's butt hole. You're a bit turned on by this revaluation. You decide to have some fun and kick at the inside of the hole. This makes Ami...
112122222.title: Stomach

132.content:
*Before I meet them*

Sailor Moon and the Sailor Scouts are fighting a new enemy, the Shrinker, she has the power to shrink girls, she has already one victim, Sailor Mars. Then after the fight the Sailor Scouts are puff out and the Shrinker has a chance to shrink them, and she did

*The Present*

It was 11:00pm and I am tired. "Man, I'm so tired, Why do my friend decide to have a birthday to 10:30pm?" I said. After I went in my house and found a box. "What the? What is a box doing here?" I said and then I decide to...
132.title: Meet the Shrinker

1322.content:
As I know what the time is now, I decide to leave the box, went to bed and go to sleep. "Man, I feel tired I really need to sleep" I said. When it reached midnight, Sailor Mars woke up and look around and see her friends have been shrunken too, she open the box and look around, she saw me, asleep. "Where are we? Who was the person whe shrunk us?" said Sailor Mars, "Maybe he will find out where we are". Sailor Mars get off the box and look down and saw a floor, she jump to my chair. "Wow, that was close" said Sailor Mars.

My chair just stop next to my bed, where I'm sleeping. "Hey, are you awake?" Sailor Mars called out to me. I didn't hear her, I was to busy sleeping and Sailor Mars is angry then she cool herself down and decide to climb to my face.

Half way through, Sailor Mars is now on my belly and when she got too close to my hands, I close my hand and woke up. "What the...Did I hear some noises? What am I holding anyway?" I said and I open my hands and saw a tiny Sailor Mars.

*Quick Note* This story when I don't know them, LOL *End of Quick Note*

"What the...Is it you who make the noises?" I said. "Well...Yeah, I did" said Sailor Mars. I look at the time, it was now 12:15am. "Look can we talk in the morning. It's late" I said and went back to sleep. "Okay" said Sailor Mars and she also went to sleep.

The Next Day. Sailor Mars woke and look around, I wasn't in my bedroom. "Where is the boy" said Sailor Mars. She jump off from my bed and onto the floor and out of my bedroom and saw me, making my breakfast and went back to my room, I went back to the kitchen to get my drink and saw Sailor Mars, who was out of bed. "I thought you got kidnapped...um...What is your name?" said Sailor Mars."My name? well my name is James and why did you think I got kidnapped?" I said. "I thought someone got you, James" said Sailor Mars. "Like who?" I said. "That strange girl, I don't know who her name is" said Sailor Mars. "Don't worry. I'm pretty sure you will remember who that girl is" I said and hold my hand out and Sailor Mars climb to my hand and I went back to my bedroom, then I notice about the box I saw last night. "I still have that box, maybe I should open it, maybe it's a trap which make me to knocked-out" I said and I open the box and saw...
1322.title: Good Night

13222.content:
As I open the box, there is nothing in here. "What the...There's nothing in here" I said. "What?!? The last time I was in the box, my friends are in here." said Sailor Mars, "Maybe my friends are looking for me after I was out of the box". "Maybe your right, whatever your are" I said. "Hey, my name is Sailor Mars! But you can call me Mars for short" said Sailor Mars. "Okay, sorry Mars. I just can't get alone with new people I don't know," I said. "It's not your fault, I have a friend which I always am angry to her everyday and I can't get alone with her" said Sailor Mars, "But I need to find my friends". "Not in this size you don’t," I said, stopping Sailor Mars on her track. "I think you right. Can you please help me find my friends?" said Sailor Mars. "No problem, I will help you," I said. "Thanks, James" said Sailor Mars.

As I look at the kitchen, Sailor Mars is looking at the lounge room and saw...
13222.title: Nothing...?

132221.content:
"Sailor Moon?" said Sailor Mars. Sailor Moon did a quiet eep sound and turn around and saw Sailor Mars. "There you are, Sailor Mars, we have been looking for you" said Sailor Moon. "You have?" said Sailor Mars. "Of course we have, we think that you have been kidnapped, again" said Sailor Moon, "No, I didn't. I'm completly safe, Sailor Moon" said Sailor Mars. "Did you found anyone, Mars" I called out, "Where could she be, she better not go missing". "Who was that and how did he know you name?" said Sailor Moon.

I walked back to my bedroom and decide to rest. "Man, I have no way to find Mars' friends. maybe I should rest" I said and I did. "I'm telling you, Mars. I think he is the one who kidnapped us" said Sailor Moon. "You crazy!? He didn't kidnapped us" said Sailor Mars. "And I think you crazy" said Sailor Moon. "Why you little..." said Sailor Mars.

A while later and I feel something moving, I open my eyes and look round and look down on my bed and saw another girl different then Mars, It was...
132221.title: Losing your mind again

info.brief_description: This story is where me and/or a Senshi from Sailor Moon have being Shrunk
info.description:
Like my last story with Sailor Moon, which is the mind control one, I decide to make a Shrinking story.

No killing

Sex is okay

No Vore

You can use either 1st person or 2nd person

If you have a fan made Sailor Senshi, make sure you have the following:
Name of Sailor Senshi plus real name
What she looks like
Age
Powers
Friends with other Sailor Senshi's
How she became a Sailor Senshi

Other then that, enjoy!
info.pretty_title: Shrinking with the Sailor Moon Senshi
